From : "ZapWorks" 
To : 19050009@student.bdu.edu.vn
Subject : A Month in AR ? July 2021 ?
? 





July 2021

Hi Hà,
It's been another busy month in the world of AR, with a huge range of experiences being created left, right and centre. 
Our amazing clients and ZapWorks users have spent July pushing the boundaries of AR with creative experiences that engage prospects, customers, and employees alike. Let's take a look at what July had in store.
READ MORE


10x10 Series One: The Finale

We closed out our first series of our 10x10 Sessions, a collection of 10-minute interviews with AR's best and brightest, with a bang this week. Watch the interview with Ash Tailor, VP Brand & Marketing at LEGOLAND, to learn all about their new AR-powered park section, LEGO MYTHICA.
WATCH THE INTERVIEW


Introducing All-New ZapWorks Training

After 10 years in the industry, we've learned a lot about what works (and what doesn't) in AR. Now, we're passing those learnings on to your business with our all-new ZapWorks Training.
You'll be guided through an immersive and holistic course that teaches you all about AR strategy and campaigns, as well as technical implementation - all with hands-on support from our award-winning Learning and Support team. 
FIND OUT MORE


ZapWorks Designer 2: Sign up for Beta Access 

As announced at our recent AR Pioneers Summit (watch the talk on-demand), the product team at Zappar have been working to rebuild ZapWorks Designer. We are now looking for early adopters to test out the new tool that we believe will serve as the future of no-code augmented reality development. If you're interested in taking part, sign up using the form below and we will be in touch with more details. 
SIGN UP


ZapWorks for Enterprise

We are proud to partner with some of the world's most innovative businesses and incorporate their feedback into our Enterprise offering.
Along with our All-New ZapWorks Training, we have also made SAML and OpenID Connect single sign on available to our Enterprise customers. This new functionality means we can continue to offer the most robust security protocols in line with our promise to help businesses scale their AR strategy with enterprise-grade security.
FIND OUT MORE

All the best 
The ZapWorks Team


My ZapWorks

Learn ZapWorks 



Zappar Ltd
